{"tid":1460655,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣召喚］世界上有兩種恐怖主義","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:19:13.000Z","uid":56239,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c821d1002536a55781bb9d56d83dabcc0e89fca","tid":1460655,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"同「世界上有兩種邏輯」一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一種叫恐怖主義<br />\n另一種叫中国式恐怖主義</span><br />\n<br />\n中共開始標籤我地係恐怖主義，然後揸正旗號用更大武力鎮壓，就算開真槍外國都冇得出聲。我地就由根本否定佢對恐怖主義的定義同西方世界嘅唔同，再之後得出佢做嘅所有嘢都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係畀外國朋友知道，所以文宣應以英文/外文為主，其次先係中文。<br />\n<br />\n嬲到震。唔好被敵人騎劫語言。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇開錯台，覺得有道理嘅請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8068fa413e65ef88076b9224ae5fe88e6cd88aee","tid":1460655,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣真係要做好準備先，佢想污名化我哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"14a58a12cc58707a8187207dce42b3990194090f","tid":1460655,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"全世界最大黑社會，冇資格講恐怖主義！<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc5f30fe7274c00f518a3980d3b7d2363fdccdf","tid":1460655,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"文宣最大問題係唔夠人多，而家好多media都充滿5毛式不盡不實嘅留言，YouTube, FB, reddit，陰啲陰啲咁用留言影響個風向<br />\n<br />\n而家仲進化到用埋英文，突然多咗好多，係海量<br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以用文宣令外國政府關注下，警惕下自己國民，又或者禁止5毛留意，咁樣用意識型態去吹風影響世界輿論同立場，對別國國家人民意識型態暗地裏改造，對國家有負面影響，會危害國家安全，好似影響人嘅取態去投要，其實應該當戰爭來看待<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解西方國家領袖視若無睹，佢哋好應該要將5毛係全世界嘅工作帶上水面，甚至要係議會正式討論，商討對策"},{"pid":"20a1fa1c2bc53bc71c1abf173912756d2e56bef5","tid":1460655,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fights for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起<span style=\"color: red;\">人道災難</span>入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span>"},{"pid":"2dca9ff1a7e056712eb58f1381c22abdeba15c63","tid":1460655,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37aa00f28a17ed847e370e6fe685fdf9b613123","tid":1460655,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好輸文宣"},{"pid":"6053c18cbf5f8e9ce8bb7b1d163550b72f8bcc2c","tid":1460655,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"CNN報導 11/8/2019 <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong isn't just battling on the streets: There is also a war on misinformation online.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cnn.it/2ZYflVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnn.it%2F2ZYflVE&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9wcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=3fd8f5e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://cnn.it/2ZYflVE</a>"},{"pid":"8cbae456dddcd27c913b9710fe4955478df13180","tid":1460655,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e5d92ae837a6b4b9a60acb6d0be279cf6caa197","tid":1460655